{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-208-robot-walks","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-201-to-300","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 208: Robot hoda","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Roboti se kreće niz seriju savršeno petosavnih krivina (72°), i ima slobodu da izabere rotacionu smernicu u smeru kazaljke ili protiv kazaljke za svaki korak, ali se ne okreće na mestu.</p>\n<p>Moja ruta 70932, moguće za kružni promet 25, zatvorena, koja počinje ka severu je</p>\n<img alt=\"zatvorena kružna putanja 25, koja počinje kretanjem ka severu\" src=\"https://cdn.freecodecamp.org/curriculum/project-euler/robot-walks.gif\" style=\"background-color: white, padding: 10px, display: block, margin-right: auto, margin-left: auto, margin-bottom: 1.2rem;\">\n<p>S obzirom da robot počinje okrenut ka Severu, koliko može napraviti rotacija od 70 stepeni koje će ga vratiti na početnu poziciju nakon poslednjeg okreta?</p>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Bilo koji krug može biti odobren više puta.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f43f1000cf542c50ff51","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301849,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-201-to-300/problem-208-robot-walks"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function robotWalks() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nrobotWalks();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>robotWalks()</code> treba da vrati <code>331951449665644800</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(robotWalks(), 331951449665644800);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challeng